policy_html:
Due to our recent acquisition we've decided to put a hold on our bug bounty program. At this time we are unable to keep up our high commitment and responsiveness that we aim for in every response.

We thank all of you for the hard work and excellent submissions thus far. We feel the bounty program has made the RelateIQ app more secure and will be looking forward to starting the program up again early next year.

If you have any security related questions please email security@relateiq.com.

Thanks,
RelateIQ Security Team

profile.about: Goodbye, Relationship Management. Hello, Relationship Intelligence.
